Hello Brendan,

I hope you're doing well.

I've rearranged the team members on the website. If you'd like to do this yourself, here's how:
  1. Log in to the WordPress Admin dashboard.
  2. Head to the "Team Members" tab.
  3. Click on "quick edit" for each team member.
  4. Adjust the "Published Date" as needed. Remember, the latest date will show up first in the Team Members section.

For more detailed instructions, you can check out our guide: Reordering Team Members on Redo Health Website

If you run into any issues or need further help, feel free to reach out.
